{"tid":2197481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"權力遊戲演員Diana Rigg (Olenna Tyrell) 在周四因癌症離世，終年 82 歲。","createTime":"2020-09-10T15:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T12:49:43.000Z","uid":32934,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f085510cd34226acb4d62c24942485c8b00d4938","tid":2197481,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200910-2220copy_uSLyA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200910-2220copy_uSLyA_1200x0.png&h=a674b8be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有份參演劇集《權力遊戲》及《復仇者》的英國女星 Diana Rigg，在周四因癌症離世，終年 82 歲。<br />\n<br />\nDiana Rigg 的經理人公司今日證實其死訊，指她在今日早上在寓所內，在家人的陪同之下安祥離世，經理人公司又呼籲外界尊重家屬的私隱。<br />\n<br />\n其女兒 Rachael Striling 指，母親在今年 3 月確診癌症，「過去的幾個月，她快樂地回顧著自己的非凡一生，充滿了愛和歡笑，並對自己職業深感自豪，我會想念她」。<br />\n<br />\nDiana Rigg 在 1961 年出演電視劇《復仇者》，並在 1969 年出演電影《007：女王密使》爆紅。近年她在《權力的遊戲》中飾演「荊棘女王」奧蓮娜雷德溫。<br />\n<br />\n她亦積極推動性別平等。她曾透露當拍攝《復仇者》時，意外發現自己的薪金比攝影師更低，她隨即爭取女性合理薪酬。在 2019 年的一次訪問中，她表示：「我被新聞界描繪成（為了反抗薪資差距的）僱傭軍，而我想要的只是平等。如今我們仍在談論性別工資差距，這是如此令人沮喪。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%83%E6%BC%94-%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2-%E9%82%A6%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%8E-diana-rigg-%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B4-82-%E6%AD%B2/?fbclid=IwAR2m88oyNzafcYD3_udFv19iclx7PUdDuNRiHaEcJpRkSfWd5EUlxu7YDjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%258F%2583%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2-%25E9%2582%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2583%258E-diana-rigg-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B4-82-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2m88oyNzafcYD3_udFv19iclx7PUdDuNRiHaEcJpRkSfWd5EUlxu7YDjA&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=a2474869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%258F%2583%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2-%25E9%2582%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2583%258E-diana-rigg-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B4-82-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2m88oyNzafcYD3_udFv19iclx7PUdDuNRiHaEcJpRkSfWd5EUlxu7YDjA&h=6c82fa9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%83%E6%BC%94-%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2-%E9%82%A6%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%8E-diana-rigg-%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B4-82-%E6%AD%B2/?fbclid=IwAR2m88oyNzafcYD3_udFv19iclx7PUdDuNRiHaEcJpRkSfWd5EUlxu7YDjA</a>"},{"pid":"33c5bed30b6192d48a164cd618d767ae7fff08b3","tid":2197481,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d181b1172b10230de919930b281b7d08b26c32c","tid":2197481,"uid":122798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"女王係套戲數一數二有腦既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67e1b099796337746f89c4aefcc917e7fbafaf8","tid":2197481,"uid":140570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e40429e66a4ebc666cae1fe495bb0e6636fa5bd","tid":2197481,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP"},{"pid":"d07a7cebe24288960621deb05d6dbc779a7f8a75","tid":2197481,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"後生靚到呢<br />\nThank you, RIP"},{"pid":"02f8b9275834e9d0f7bee12acf515aa380630eb1","tid":2197481,"uid":144275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"